                "description": {
                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature moves within 10 feet of the section of floor from which the choir can arise.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The choir rises, and its song deals [[/r 4d8+18 #mental]]{4d8+18 mental damage} to non-evil creatures within 30 feet of the souls' spectral forms. Affected creatures must each attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"24\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,damaging-effect,emotion,enchantment,fear,mental,occult\" data-pf2-label=\"Profane Chant DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage. It also becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 3} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fleeing]{Fleeing} for 1 round.</p>\n</div>"
